cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on visual recognition of product classes in grocery stores using smartphone images. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of active learning to improve recognition accuracy. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for product class recognition. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper aims to improve the shopping experience for visually impaired shoppers. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions building a mapping of words to product classes based on a dataset.
